	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Loop point detection is tricky. Songs that loop and change after several repetitions, such as the special world theme from Super Mario World, complicate matters. Ultimately the right solution is something that encodes a length in the file itself. Does NSFE do this?

		

